      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It's understandable to wonder if there's a way to break free from the cycle, but unfortunately, life doesn't always provide easy answers. Many people find that the pain of losing someone is a journey that takes time, and it's okay to not be okay. Allow yourself to accept that the grief is a part of your life right now, and that it may take time to heal, even if it doesn't feel like it.",
